page.title: 16Armed Forces, Aircraft
page.content: Every so often Military planes fly over,some of them fly extremely low over the houses.A lot of the villagers complain about the noise,the planes circle round over the villages to Cowden bombing range .Most of the planes are A10 TANKBUSTERS,JAGUARS and TORNADOS.It is a spectacle for the people who plane spot around the village.The village is also a part of a route used by the Army school of Mechanical Transport,they come from Leconfield and most of the cadets are learning to drive personnel carriers,and about engines.{
